ylor II|pos=DL}}\n{{American football roster/Player|num=92|class=SO|first=Elias|last=Hale|pos=DL}}\n{{American football roster/Player|num=93|class=FR|first=Isaiah|last=Nichols|pos=DL}}\n{{American football roster/Player|num=95|class=SR|first=Jake|last=Hall|pos=DL}}\n{{American football roster/Player|num=97|class=SO|first=Brandon|last=DePrato|pos=DL}}\n\n|special_teams_players=\n{{American football roster/Player|num=18|class=JR|first=Blake|last=Johnson|pos=P}}\n{{American football roster/Player|num=19|class=JR|first=Connor|last=Limpert|pos=K}}\n{{American football roster/Player|num=43|class=JR|first=George|last=Madden|pos=LS}}\n{{American football roster/Player|num=48|class=FR|rs=y|first=Jordan|last=Silver|pos=LS}}\n{{American football roster/Player|num=92|class=SO|first=Chad|last=Stephens|pos=P}}\n}}\n{{American football roster/Footer|roster_url=http://www.arkansasrazorbacks.com/sport/m-footbl/roster/|accessdate=July 17, 2018\n|head_coach=\n*[[Chad Morris]]\n|asst_coach=\n*[[Joe Craddock]] (OC)\n*[[John Chavis (American football)|John Chavis]] (DC)\n}}\n\n===Team captains===\nPrior to the season, Coach Chad Morris announced that permanent captains would not be announced until later in the season, and the captain spots would rotate until then.\n\n*'''Week 1 vs. EIU:''' #51 Hjalte Froholdt (senior OL), #1 Jared Cornelius (senior WR), #9 Santos Ramirez (senior DB), #8 De'Jon Harris (junior LB), #23 Dre Greenlaw (senior LB)<ref>{{cite web |title=Razorback Football on Twitter - Week 1 captains |url=https://twitter.com/RazorbackFB/status/1035300054708445184 |website=Twitter |accessdate=August 30, 2018 |language=en}}</ref>\n*'''Week 2 vs. CSU:''' #91 Michael Taylor II (senior DL), #90 Armon Watts (senior DL), #60 Brian Wallace (senior OL), #18 Jeremy Patton (senior TE)<ref>{{cite web |title=Razorback Football on Twitter - Week 2 captains |url=https://twitter.com/RazorbackFB/status/1037871659867365376 |website=Twitter |accessdate=September 7, 2018 |language=en}}</ref>\n*'''